<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-1574] Bootstrapping is broken</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1574</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Bootstrap doesn&apos;t block for streaming requests which means nodetool move isn&apos;t blocking.  More importantly bootstrap fails to call finishBootstrapping if no stream requests are ever made. This means its impossible to perform moves if you have no keyspaces.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12475799">CASSANDRA-1574</key>
            <summary>Bootstrapping is broken</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
